documentation.text:
@title ForwarderFactory
 @dev A factory contract to deploy multiple Forwarder contracts.
@dev Returns the total number of Forwarder contracts deployed.

devdoc.details: A factory contract to deploy multiple Forwarder contracts.

createForwarder(address).details: Deploys a new Forwarder contract with the specified pool address.

params._pool: The address of the pool to which the Forwarder will send ETH.

returns._0: The address of the newly deployed Forwarder contract.

getForwarder(uint256).details: Retrieves a Forwarder contract by index.

params.index: The index in the forwarders array.

returns._0: The Forwarder contract at the specified index.

getForwardersCount().details: Returns the total number of Forwarder contracts deployed.

devdoc.title: ForwarderFactory
